[[Image:Glutathione-3D-vdW.png|thumb|right|250px|Model of the antioxidant [[metabolomics|metabolite]] [[glutathione]]. The yellow sphere is the [[redox|redox-active]] sulfur atom that provides antioxidant activity, while the red, blue, white, and dark grey spheres represent oxygen, nitrogen, hydrogen, and carbon atoms, respectively.]]

