Hello!  I would like to exchange links with you, if that''s possible.  Wikipedia and Nupedia are free, open content encyclopedias.  Wikipedia now has about 10,000 articles, including many in the life sciences, and Nupedia''s (peer reviewed) biology category is its most active.

